#: skgbankmodeler/skgunitobject.cpp:2215
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Description test for a text file used to define a source of download"
msgid ""
"The URL or the SCRIPT of the source. %1 will be replaced by the internet "
"code of the unit"
msgstr ""
"De URL of het script van de bron. %1 zal worden vervangen door de "
"internetcode van de eenheid"

#: skgbankmodeler/skgunitobject.cpp:2220
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Description test for a text file used to define a source of download"
msgid "%1 will be replaced by the current day in format yyyy-MM-dd"
msgstr "%1 zal worden vervangen door de huidige dag in het formaat yyyy-MM-dd"

#: skgbankmodeler/skgunitobject.cpp:2225
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Description test for a text file used to define a source of download"
msgid "%1 will be replaced by the previous date in format yyyy-MM-dd"
msgstr ""
"%1 zal worden vervangen door de huidige datum in het formaat yyyy-MM-dd"

#: skgbankmodeler/skgunitobject.cpp:2234
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Description test for a text file used to define a source of download"
msgid ""
"The mode (HTML or CSV or CSVR). In HTML mode, only one value will be "
"extracted from downloaded page. In CSV mode, a value per line will be "
"extracted. CSVR means CSV in reverse mode."
msgstr ""
"De modus (HTML of CSV of CSVR). In HTML-modus, zal slechts één waarde worden "
"opgehaald van de gedownloade pagina. In CSV-modus, zal een waarde per regel "
"worden opgehaald. CSVR betekent CSV in omgekeerde modus."

#: skgbankmodeler/skgunitobject.cpp:2241
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Description test for a text file used to define a source of download"
msgid "The regular expression for the price (see %1)"
msgstr "De reguliere expressie voor de prijs (zie %1)"

#: skgbankmodeler/skgunitobject.cpp:2248
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Description test for a text file used to define a source of download"
